:children.type: (fields: Field[], operation: { add, remove, move }, meta: { errors }) => React.ReactNode

:initialValue.description: Set default values for child elements. If it conflicts with Form's initialValues, Form takes precedence
:initialValue.description_zh: 设置子元素默认值，如果与 Form 的 initialValues 冲突则以 Form 为准

:name.description: Field name, supports arrays. The List itself is also a field, so getFieldsValue() returns all values under List by default, you can change this behavior through parameters
:name.description_zh: 字段名，支持数组。List 本身也是字段，因而 getFieldsValue() 默认会返回 List 下所有值，你可以通过参数改变这一行为

:rules.description: Validation rules, only supports custom rules. Need to be used with ErrorList together.
:rules.description_zh: 校验规则，仅支持自定义规则。需要配合 ErrorList 一同使用。

rootClassName.description: Add className to the outermost layer of component
rootClassName.description_zh: 添加在组件最外层的 className

Field.name: key
Field.description: The unique key of the field

Field.name: name
Field.description: The field name (index of the array)

Field.name: fieldKey
Field.description: The unique field key with the meta information
Field.description_zh: 带有元信息的字段唯一标识

Operation.name: add
Operation.description: Add a field to the end of the array or at specified position
Operation.description_zh: 添加一个字段到数组末尾或指定位置

Operation.name: remove
Operation.description: Remove a field at the specified index
Operation.description_zh: 删除指定索引位置的字段

Operation.name: move
Operation.description: Move a field from one index to another
Operation.description_zh: 将字段从一个位置移动到另一个位置

Meta.name: errors
Meta.description: Error information for the current field
